102
00:08:14,744 --> 00:08:16,121
Apakah dia meninggalkanku begitu saja di sini?

103
00:08:22,168 --> 00:08:23,420
Brengsek.

104
00:08:25,130 --> 00:08:26,423
Shin Seo-ri.

105
